      "options": {
        "content": "## Router Overview\nRaw `telephon` metrics are shown separately from RabbitMQ queue depth and derived metrics.\n\nPanels prefixed with **Approx** use `telephon` timing summaries that are reconstructed from rolling averages and should be treated as operational approximations, not formula-grade source-of-truth values. `approx_score_router_seconds` is router-service context only and is not the fast-vs-heavy path decision score.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
